{
  "stem": "1502.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were talking about the raids that they started on Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before I go into the Final Solution for the Jews in Belgium, I have to mention that as the laws against Jews started to be applied to Belgium, what followed the anti-Jewish laws was the establishment of the Gestapo headquarters special section for Jews on one of the main streets in Brussels-- also one of the nicest, and most elegant avenues in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was Avenue Louise.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's where they established a headquarters in a huge building, which is-- still today has a commemorative plaque.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the center-- the headquarters-- for the destruction of the Belgian, the Belgian Jewry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's where it all came from.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They established themselves there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The system was the same all over Europe, as we learned later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wanted-- and they did-- establish a Jewish committee, a committee of permanent Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That made their work a lot easier because how would they know every Jew in the city?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's only the Jews that knew where the Jews are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they established-- they got in touch, somehow, with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some were prominent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most of them were not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of them were people that, in the community, were completely unknown.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were, most of them-- I wouldn't say most of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them were refugees from Austria, Jewish refugees from Austria or Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had-- very easy to communicate with them because they were speaking their language.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These Jews that they picked for the committee-- one of them, the president of the committee, was a certain Blum.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a Jewish a business man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was an assimilated Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had nothing to do, really, with any Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was very wealthy and he was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
